OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBank of England moving     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcloser to interest rate cut
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England has held interest  
OL,6, rates at 5.25% but indicated it is     
OL,7, edging towards cutting borrowing costs.
OL,9,FAt its latest meeting, the Bank said it
OL,10,Fhad discussed cutting rates, with      
OL,11,Finflation - the pace of price rises -  
OL,12,Fset to fall quickly this year.         
OL,14,FBut the Bank's governor said it would  
OL,15,Fwait for firm evidence that inflation  
OL,16,Fwas under control before doing so.     
OL,18,FFor the first time since the 2020 Covid
OL,19,Fpandemic, one Bank policymaker voted   
OL,20,Ffor an immediate cut.                  
